OL,3,CWomen from Afghanistan restart their
OL,4,Ceducation in Wales after motherhood
OL,6,FFamilies who left Afghanistan for
OL,7,FWales almost 15 years ago have been
OL,8,Frestarting their education.
OL,10,FKiran Cymru has been supporting
OL,11,FShabnam Tajpoor and Tamana Nisar Ahmed
OL,12,Fin restarting their education to
OL,13,Fbecome bookkeepers.
OL,15,FWhen Tamana and Shabnam got started,
OL,16,Fthey had no idea how much the new
OL,17,Fchallenge would offer them.
OL,19,FShabnam came to Wales from Afghanistan
OL,20,Fin 2011. She says this education has
OL,21,Fgiven her a lot of confidence.
