OL,6,FShe said: "I'm starting my studies
OL,7,Fafter a very long time. I had dropped
OL,8,Fit because of my kids. I have three
OL,9,Fyoung kids, so I didn't continue and
OL,10,Fafter a long time, I've started my
OL,11,Fstudies now.
OL,13,F"I didn't know too much about it but I
OL,14,Freally enjoyed it. I don't know but I
OL,15,Fthink my future is very bright, maybe
OL,16,FI'll do lots of things in the future."
