OL,3,CWomen from Afghanistan restart their
OL,4,Ceducation in Wales after motherhood
OL,6,FKiran Cymru is a grassroots charity
OL,7,Fwhich provides free services to
OL,8,Ffamilies including education for
OL,9,Fchildren and adults, such as
OL,10,Fbookkeeping and computer programming
OL,11,Flike Python training.
OL,13,FTamana came to Wales from Afghanistan
OL,14,F15 years ago with her husband.
OL,16,FShe said: "I joined Kiran Cymru
OL,17,Fstraight after lockdown. I was looking
OL,18,Ffor something that the whole family
OL,19,Fcan join in, including the children
OL,20,Fand adults altogether.
