OL,3,CWomen from Afghanistan restart their
OL,4,Ceducation in Wales after motherhood
OL,6,F"They are supporting us and they are
OL,7,Fgiving us chances to improve our life
OL,8,Fand to become the best of who we are."
OL,10,FBut building trust was not easy for
OL,11,Fthe founders of the charity, who want
OL,12,Fto empower more families.
OL,14,FCo-founder Anirban Mukhopadhyay said:
OL,15,F"People will trust you and think that
OL,16,Fit is worthy of giving you their time
OL,17,Ffor taking our services only when they
OL,18,Fhave seen the benefit of taking our
OL,19,Fservices before their eyes."
