OL,6,FKiran Cymru's Tamasree Mukhopadhyay
OL,7,Fsaid: "We looked after these families
OL,8,Fas their own family and we built up
OL,9,Ftheir confidence gradually.
OL,11,F"It takes longer to build up the trust
OL,12,Ffirst. So, we can tell them 'look, you
OL,13,Fare comfortable' and 'look, anything
OL,14,Fthat you have got in your mind you can
OL,15,Fshare'."
OL,17,FWhile balancing studying alongside
OL,18,Fmotherhood, Tamana and Shabnam'
OL,19,Fchildren say they are proud of what
OL,20,Ftheir mums are achieving.
